p.m."], "Thursday": ["5 a.m.–9 p.m."], "Tuesday": ["5 a.m.–9 p.m."], "Wednesday": ["5 a.m.–9 p.m."]}'::jsonb, '[{"Name": "Anna Belz", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4nCNG5MHttTQUVF622r2-p6U9Q7D3IkRjPc22F2kTur1DUTwc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100", "Rating": 4, "Description": "The downside of the court is that there''s no net between the courts, just a low fence with gaps where the ball rolls. It''s very inconvenient, especially if you''re a beginner. The ball constantly flies into the next court.\nThe courts are large, with plenty of room on the sides and back. However, it was stuffy and hot at 3-4 p.m. The roofs were closed, and the roof on Court 1 doesn''t open at all, so I wouldn''t recommend Court 1.", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn27bnKCYkiCT2hvOL_HRFUeSfvxCrufdv497RjuEMvj364009xWo8aewECCe_io70IfIUtAd8kylhEVUrvMl6O7Ytaq9t984MRTZLu8VRyrD9Wlxl4Fya8DpAryIPSI8mBERZskQ72kWUO3=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3yo921MzJt7GrdI5Xh0_ZN30O2XIJ46eFmVYtgX5XIBB_0y21k-oEc-0JWHoq09pqRcidwz05LsBDeLxumyJ241JRYV3FjNgl_OzNOhXv67tixLSPU-gX7rb4RYxyL5FWndO_syTF8eUw7=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0WEAFX7MwUEVO6mTSmlpeEnT_ObSvcfK8FSiuhxUXilZrsdkTjCAW5RiyuJY0z5xfv7yv08rQznE2DfpS-0awOoo2BShd-EI7G-rHmckHVYnEXetCpA2OBFy-xRZYx5YIHztdaDHrmAzQ-=k-no"], "When": "2026-3-7"}, {"Name": "anna suldina", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIk7jEv7UTC0NM0cMRBI2RBy9IpCF5I6ic4U1jSB0qcJJsWJA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "great pickleball court! 1 hour - 140 000, with the rental of rackets", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "Gina Lannin", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXpamFfQmJaEmjfAgn8HZstTpElEXQrdzVsOope0TTP78D-WzI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100", "Rating": 4, "Description": "Courts are nice, and ceilings are high so they don''t interfere with lobs, but the low barriers between courts don''t prevent stray balls very well.